<section id="our-promise">
  <h2>
    <span class="section-icon">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M19 14c1.49-1.46 3-3.21 3-5.5A5.5 5.5 0 0 0 16.5 3c-1.76 0-3 .5-4.5 2-1.5-1.5-2.74-2-4.5-2A5.5 5.5 0 0 0 2 8.5c0 2.3 1.5 4.05 3 5.5l7 7Z"/></svg>
    </span>
    Our Promise
  </h2>
  
  <p class="lead">We remember your story because that's how we help you grow. Not to sell it. Not to share it. To be there for you in a way no one else can.</p>
  
  <div class="callout callout--warm">
    <strong>The Ferni difference:</strong>
    <p>We're not like social media or search engines that make money from your data. Our business model is simple—you pay for our service, and we use your information only to make that service better for you.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="what-we-remember">
  <h2>
    <span class="section-icon">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M21 15a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z"/></svg>
