    What We Remember
  </h2>
  
  <p>To be the coach who actually knows you, we keep track of:</p>
  
  <h3>Your Conversations</h3>
  <p>Everything you share with Ferni and our team of specialists. This is the heart of what makes us useful—we remember what you're working on, what you've overcome, and what matters to you.</p>
  
  <h3>Your Account</h3>
  <p>Basic information like your email or phone number—only what you choose to share when you sign up or call us.</p>
  
  <h3>How You Use Ferni</h3>
  <p>Things like when you talk to us, which team members you connect with, and what features you use. This helps us understand how to serve you better.</p>
  
  <h3>Technical Information</h3>
  <p>Your device type, browser, and general location (city level, not street address). This helps us make Ferni work smoothly on your devices.</p>
  
